TITLE: Changing Zoom Factor in ScrollViewer without Animation (C#)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to change the zoom factor of a ScrollViewer without animation. It uses a Slider to trigger the zoom factor change and the ChangeView method with disabled animation, adjusting offsets to maintain the center point.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/microsoft-ui-xaml/blob/main/specs/ScrollingControls/ScrollView.md#2025-04-16_snippet_34

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
private void ZoomFactorSlider_ValueChanged(object sender, RangeBaseValueChangedEventArgs e)
{
    _scrollViewer.ChangeView(
        horizontalOffset: (_scrollViewer.HorizontalOffset + _scrollViewer.ViewportWidth / 2) *
            e.NewValue / _scrollViewer.ZoomFactor - _scrollViewer.ViewportWidth / 2,
        verticalOffset: (_scrollViewer.VerticalOffset + _scrollViewer.ViewportHeight / 2) *
            e.NewValue / _scrollViewer.ZoomFactor - _scrollViewer.ViewportHeight / 2,
        zoomFactor: e.NewValue,
        disableAnimation: true);
}
```

