TITLE: Stopping Thumb Animation in C#
DESCRIPTION: Stops the currently running thumb animation for the specified orientation. This halts the translation animation on the X or Y axis of the interaction visual.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/microsoft-ui-xaml/blob/main/specs/ScrollingControls/ScrollPresenter.md#2025-04-16_snippet_49

LANGUAGE: C#
CODE:
```
private void StopThumbAnimation(Orientation orientation)
{
    if (interactionVisual != null)
    {
        if (orientation == Orientation.Horizontal)
        {
            interactionVisual.StopAnimation("Translation.X");
        }
        else
        {
            interactionVisual.StopAnimation("Translation.Y");
        }
    }
}
```

